#: ../../sales/products_prices/prices/B2B_B2C.rst:23
msgid "This would do **8.26€ (taxes excluded)** and a **tax of 1.74€**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../sales/products_prices/prices/B2B_B2C.rst:25
